Class InAppCampaign

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.localytics.android.Campaign
      • com.localytics.android.InAppCampaign
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public final class InAppCampaign
extends Campaign
    The in-app campaign class from which user can get the in-app campaign information. An in-app campaign object is passed to the user through the messaging listener.
